---
import { Picture } from 'astro:assets'
import imgTalk from '../assets/talk1.webp'
---

<section class='relative bg-white dark:bg-zinc-900' aria-labelledby='expertise-heading'>
	<div class='mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-24 lg:px-8 lg:py-32'>
		<div class='flex flex-col gap-16 lg:flex-row lg:items-start lg:justify-between'>
			{/* Left Column */}
			<div class='flex flex-col lg:w-[40%]'>
				<h2
					id='expertise-heading'
					class='text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 sm:text-4xl'
				>
					My expertise
				</h2>

				<p class='mt-6 text-lg font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400'>
					I'm a freelance backend developer and I've been working on several projects for the past
					years.
				</p>

				<Picture
					src={imgTalk}
					alt='Speaking at a tech conference'
					width={800}
					height={800}
					formats={['avif', 'webp']}
					class='mt-12 aspect-4/3 w-full rounded-3xl object-cover grayscale lg:aspect-3/4 lg:h-[40rem] object-top'
					loading='lazy'
					decoding='async'
				/>
			</div>

			{/* Right Column */}
			<div class='lg:w-[50%]'>
				<h3 class='sr-only'>Services offered</h3>
				<ul class='space-y-12 divide-y divide-zinc-100 dark:divide-zinc-800'>
					<li class='pt-12 first:pt-0'>
						<article class='group relative'>
							<h4 class='text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100'>
								Expert Backend Solutions
							</h4>
							<p class='mt-4 text-base/relaxed font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400'>
								Do you need high-quality backend solutions? As an experienced Golang developer, I
								craft robust backends with high unit/integration test coverage, ensuring excellent
								performance with fast deployment and a small binary.
							</p>
						</article>
					</li>
					<li class='pt-12'>
						<article class='group relative'>
							<h4 class='text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100'>
								Low-JS, High-Performance Websites
							</h4>
							<p class='mt-4 text-base/relaxed font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400'>
								Want captivating, low-footprint websites? I create visually stunning, highly
								performant sites using Astro and HTMX. These technologies are perfect for
								cost-effective solutions that don't sacrifice speed or functionality.
							</p>
						</article>
					</li>
					<li class='pt-12'>
						<article class='group relative'>
							<h4 class='text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100'>
								Performance Optimization Specialist
							</h4>
							<p class='mt-4 text-base/relaxed font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400'>
								Do you need high-performance backend solutions? I specialize in crafting efficient
								systems with optimized data structures, minimal allocations, and comprehensive
								benchmarking. My solutions are built for scale, ensuring maximum throughput with
								minimal resource usage.
							</p>
						</article>
					</li>
					<li class='pt-12'>
						<article class='group relative'>
							<h4 class='text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100'>
								Cloud Infrastructure Development
							</h4>
							<p class='mt-4 text-base/relaxed font-medium text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400'>
								Looking for scalable cloud solutions? I develop cloud-native applications with a
								focus on containerization and microservices architecture. Using modern DevOps
								practices, I create reliable, scalable systems that grow with your needs.
							</p>
						</article>
					</li>
				</ul>

				<div class='mt-12 flex border-t border-zinc-100 pt-6 dark:border-zinc-800'>
					<a
						href='/resume'
						class='group inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-base font-medium text-teal-500 hover:text-teal-600 dark:text-teal-400 dark:hover:text-teal-300'
					>
						View my experiences
						<span aria-hidden='true' class='transition group-hover:translate-x-1'>â†’</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
